      "author": "Jareika",
      "description": "### Changes\r\n\r\n- **Simple View durations reworked**\r\n  - Durations in the simple list view are no longer computed by fully decoding every audio file via Web Audio.\r\n  - Instead, the plugin now:\r\n    - loads only metadata via a temporary `<audio>` element,\r\n    - caches the duration (seconds) together with file size and mtime,\r\n    - and stores this cache persistently in the plugin data.\r\n  - A small queue limits the number of concurrent metadata loads, so even folders with hundreds of tracks no longer cause high CPU/RAM usage when the simple view is opened or when switching folders.\r\n\r\n- **Quick Play command**\r\n  - New command: **“Quick play sound (modal)”**.\r\n  - Opens a modal search box that lets you type a title and instantly play a sound from the library, without navigating the soundboard view.\r\n  - Handles duplicates by file name by showing each title only once (first match wins), which keeps the list compact even if the same sound exists in multiple theme folders.\r\n  - All existing playback rules are respected (per‑sound prefs, fades, loop flag, ambience volume, allow‑overlap setting).",
      "downloadCount": 12,
      "draft": false,
      "name": "TTRPG Soundboard",
      "prerelease": false,
